  <chunk id="5e1989bee9ae95c79dea0e12d9f455cb1d2b61d5.c2" text="Conclusion: Study of transcriptomic signatures in blood suggests an essential role of neutrophil proteases in COPD patients with critical respiratory illness. Measurement and modulation of the expression of these genes could present an option for clinical monitoring and treatment of severe COPD exacerbations.">
